  "title": "Data Analyst (SQL_Python_DataManagement_Finance)",
  "description": "<p>Maltem Asia is seeking a <strong>Data Analyst </strong>for a Wealth Management Client based in Singapore.<br /></p><p><strong>Summary:</strong></p><ul><li>Supporting data management operations activities for Data Cloud project and initiatives.</li></ul><p><br /><strong>Must have Skillsets:</strong></p><ul><li>Possess a degree in Computer Science/Information Technology or related fields.</li><li>3 to 7 years of working experience in Data Management, especially in financial industry.</li><li>Ability to manage data reconciliation/quality checks (implementation, monitoring, and troubleshooting).</li><li>Strong hands-on experience in data analysis.</li><li><strong>Proficiency in SQL and Python.</strong></li><li>Experience in managing SLA and queries from end users.</li><li>Experience in providing documentation support, e.g. in technical/functional specifications.</li><li>Strong problem solving and communication skills with stakeholders.</li><li>Detail-oriented with a focus on quality and accuracy.</li><li>Ability to manage multiple tasks and priorities in a fast-paced environment.</li></ul>",
